data.description: Take a look at this gorgeous 4 bedroom home located in the highly desirable community of Rosena Ranch.  Downstairs you will find upgraded flooring throughout the open floor concept.  The kitchen opens up to the family room and dining area where the backyard has a large covered patio.  Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms including the master suite.  In the community itself you will find a community center with 2 pools, fitness center, bbq area, kids splash park, playground, sports courts and a K-8 school.
